m=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"> ty chn Trnh hng dn thit lp</a>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Chn cch bn mun c thanh ton</strong>. Qun l thanh ton mt cch thun tin ngay ti ca hng ca bn vi <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/payments/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WooPayments</a> (C sn trong Hoa K, Anh, Ireland, c, New Zealand, Canada, Ty Ban Nha, Php, c v ). Chp nhn th tn dng, v di ng, chuyn khon ngn hng v tin mt mt cch an ton nh <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/product-category/woocommerce-extensions/payment-gateways/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Hn 100 cng thanh ton</a>  bao gm <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/stripe/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Stripe</a>, <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/woocommerce-gateway-paypal-checkout/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">PayPal</a>, v <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/square/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Square</a>.</li>\n<li><strong>nh cu hnh cc ty chn vn chuyn ca bn</strong>. In nhn USPS ngay t trang tng quan ca bn v thm ch ln lch nhn hng vi <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/shipping/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WooCommerce Shipping</a> (ch  Hoa K). Kt ni vi <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/product-category/woocommerce-extensions/shipping-methods/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">cc nh mng ni ting</a> chng hn nh UPS v FedEx  cng vi nhiu gii php giao hng, kim k v x l n hng a dng cho a phng ca bn.</li>\n<li><strong>n gin ha thu bn hng</strong>. Thm <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/tax/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Thu WooCommerce</a> hoc <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/product-category/woocommerce-extensions/tax?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">cc dch v tch hp tng t</a>  bin cc php tnh t ng thnh hin thc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Pht trin doanh nghip ca bn, thm tnh nng v gim st ca hng ca bn khi ang di chuyn</h4>\n<p>WooCommerce l cng c kinh doanh chuyn nghip. Theo di cc ch s hiu sut quan trng nht i vi bn bng bng iu khin trung tm mnh m v linh hot c tch hp trong WooCommerce.</p>\n<p>M rng i tng ca bn trn cc knh tip th v x hi bng <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/google-ads/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Google Ads</a>, <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/hubspot-for-woocommerce/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">HubSpot</a>, <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/mailchimp-for-woocommerce/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Mailchimp</a>, v <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/facebook/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Facebook</a> Tch hp. Bn lun c th kim tra <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/marketing-hub/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Trung tm tip th</a> trong bng iu khin  c nhng  tng v mo mi gip bn thnh cng.</p>\n<p>Nng cao chc nng ca ca hng vi hng trm tin ch m rng min ph v tr ph t <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WooCommerce Marketplace</a>. Cc nh pht trin ca chng ti <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/marketplace-overview/#section-6?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">kim tra tng tin ch m rng mi</a> v thng xuyn xem xt cc tin ch m rng hin c  duy tr cc tiu chun cht lng ca Marketplace. Chng ti ang tch cc <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/marketplace-overview/#section-2?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">tm kim cc sn phm gip ngi xy dng ca hng to ra cc ca hng thnh cng</a>.</p>\n<p>Qun l ca hng ca bn t mi ni vi <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/mobile/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">ng dng di ng</a> min ph WooCommerce (Android v iOS ). Cnh bo tit l ni dung: Hy   n m thanh thng bo &#8220;cha-ching&#8221; hi gy nghin mi khi bn thc hin mt t bn hng mi!</p>\n<h4>S hu v kim sot d liu ca hng ca bn  mi mi</h4>\n<p>Vi <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/woocommerce/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WooCommerce</a>, d liu ca bn thuc v bn. Lun lun.</p>\n<p>Nu chn chia s <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/usage-tracking/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">d liu s dng</a> vi chng ti, bn c th cm nhn c t tin khi bit rng n c n danh v gi an ton. Chn khng tham gia bt c lc no m khng nh hng n ca hng ca bn.</p>\n<p>Khng ging nh cc gii php thng mi in t c lu tr, d liu ca hng WooCommerce c tnh minh bch trong tng lai; bn c th t do xut tt c ni dung ca mnh v a trang web ca mnh n bt k nn tng no bn chn. Khng c hn ch.</p>\n<h4>Ti sao cc nh pht trin chn (v yu thch) WooCommerce</h4>\n<p>Nh pht trin c th s dng <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/woocommerce/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WooCommerce</a>  to, ty chnh v m rng quy m ca hng nhm p ng cc thng s k thut chnh xc ca khch hng, thc hin cc ci tin thng qua tin ch m rng hoc gii php ty chnh.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tn dng <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/introduction-to-hooks-actions-and-filters/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">hooks v cc b lc</a>  sa i hoc to ra chc nng.</li>\n<li>Tch hp hu nh mi dch v bng cch s dng <a href=\"https://developer.woocommerce.com/docs/getting-started-with-the-woocommerce-rest-api/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">REST API</a> mnh m v webhooks.</li>\n<li>Thit k v xy dng cc khi ni dung ty chnh vi React.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.woocommerce.com/docs/category/extension-development/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Kim tra v sa i</a> bt k phn no ca m plugin ct li.</li>\n<li>Tng tc qu trnh pht trin vi <a href=\"https://developer.woocommerce.com/docs/category/wc-cli/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">CLI</a> cc nhanh.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nn tng ct li c th nghim nghim ngt v thng xuyn, c h tr bi mt nhm pht trin chuyn dng lm vic trn nhiu mi gi. Ti liu ton din c cp nht vi mi bn pht hnh, trao quyn cho bn  xy dng chnh xc ca hng cn thit.</p>\n<h4>Hy l mt phn ca cng ng ton cu ang pht trin ca chng ti</h4>\n<p>WooCommerce c mt cng ng ln mnh, y nhit huyt, tn tm gip  cc nh bn hng thnh cng &#8211; v cng ng ny ang pht trin nhanh chng.</p>\n<p>C <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/meetups/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Cuc gp g WooCommerce</a> ti cc a im trn khp th gii m bn c th tham d min ph v thm ch tham gia chy b. Nhng s kin ny l mt cch tuyt vi  hc hi t nhng ngi khc, chia s chuyn mn ca bn v kt ni vi nhng ngi cng ch hng.</p>\n<p>WooCommerce cng thng xuyn hin din ti cc s kin WordCamp trn ton cu &#8211; chng ti rt mun c gp bn.</p>\n<h4>ng gp v dch</h4>\n<p>WooCommerce c pht trin v h tr bi Automattic, ngi to ra WordPress.com v Jetpack. Chng ti cng c hng trm cng tc vin c lp v lun c nhiu c hi hn na. Hy truy cp <a href=\"https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Kho lu tr WooCommerce GitHub</a>  tm hiu cch bn c th tham gia .</p>\n<p>WooCommerce c dch sang nhiu ngn ng, bao gm ting an Mch, ting Ukraina v ting Ba T. Gip bn a ha WooCommerce hn na bng cch thm ngn ng ca bn  truy cp <a href=\"https://translate.wordpress.org/projects/wp-plugins/woocommerce/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"> dch.wordpress.org</a>.</p>\n<h4>Kt ni vi WooCommerce.com</h4>\n<p>Bn c th kt ni ca hng ca mnh vi <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">WooCommerce.com</a>  qun l ng k ca bn trn WooCommerce Marketplace v nhn bn cp nht sn phm m khng cn ri khi trang qun tr WordPress. Kt ni cng cho php ci t cc sn phm  mua trc tip t WooCommerce.com v n gin ha vic truy cp h tr k thut. Nu bn mun tm hiu v loi d liu no c thu thp v cch s dng d liu , vui lng tham kho <a href=\"https://automattic.com/privacy/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Chnh sch Bo mt</a> ca chng ti.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:3070:\"<h4>Yu cu ti thiu</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Yu cu PHP 7.4 tr ln (khuyn ngh PHP 8.0 tr ln)</li>\n<li>Yu cu MySQL 5.5.5 tr ln, HOC MariaDB phin bn 10.1 tr ln</li>\n<li>WordPress 6.8 or greater</li>\n<li>(Khuyn ngh) Gii hn <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/increasing-the-wordpress-memory-limit/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">b nh</a> WordPress t 256 MB tr ln.</li>\n<li>(Khuyn ngh) H tr <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/ssl-and-https/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">HTTPS</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Ci t t ng</h4>\n<p>Ci t t ng l ty chn d dng nht &#8212; WordPress s x l vic truyn tp v bn s khng cn phi ri khi trnh duyt web ca mnh.  thc hin ci t t ng WooCommerce, hy ng nhp vo bng iu khin WordPress ca bn, iu hng n menu Plugin v nhp vo Thm mi.</p>\n<p>Trong trng tm kim, hy nhp WooCommerce, sau  nhp vo Tm kim Plugin. Sau khi bn  tm thy chng ti, bn c th xem chi tit v plugin nh im pht hnh, nh gi v m t. iu quan trng nht tt nhin l bn c th ci t n! Nhp vo Ci t ngay by gi v WordPress s thc hin phn cn li.</p>\n<h4>Ci t th cng</h4>\n<p>Phng php ci t th cng yu cu ti xung plugin WooCommerce v ti n ln my ch web thng qua ng dng FTP yu thch ca bn. Codex WordPress bao gm <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/article/managing-plugins/#manual-plugin-installation\" rel=\"ugc\">hng dn v cch thc hin ci t th cng ti y</a>.</p>\n<h4>ang cp nht</h4>\n<p>Cc bn cp nht t ng s hot ng trn tru, nhng chng ti vn khuyn bn nn sao lu trang web ca mnh.</p>\n<p>Nu bn gp s c vi trang ca hng/danh mc sau khi cp nht, thit lp li permalinks bng cch truy cp WordPress &gt; Ci t &gt; Permalinks v nhn Lu. iu  s khin mi th tr li bnh thng.</p>\n<h4>D liu mu</h4>\n<p>WooCommerce i km vi mt s d liu mu m bn c th s dng  xem sn phm trng nh th no; nhp sample_products.xml qua <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-importer/\" rel=\"ugc\">trnh nhp WordPress</a>. Bn cng c th s dng <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/product-csv-importer-exporter/?utm_source=wp%20org%20repo%20listing&amp;utm_content=3.6\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">trnh nhp CSV</a> hoc ca chng ti <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/products/product-csv-import-suite/?utm_source=wp%20org%20repo%20listing&amp;utm_content=3.6\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">tin ch m rng B nhp CSV</a> ca chng ti  nhp sample_products.csv</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:9254:\"\n<dt id=\"where%20can%20i%20find%20woocommerce%20documentation%20and%20user%20guides%3F\">\nTi c th tm ti liu v hng dn s dng  u?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p> c tr gip thit lp v nh cu hnh WooCommerce, vui lng tham kho <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/documentation/plugins/woocommerce/getting-started/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp