olm Co-working Space, quy t gn 30 thnh vin l cc lp trnh vin, marketer, ch doanh nghip, blogger v nhng ngi yu thch WordPress. y l s kin c mong ch nht nm ca cng ng, ni [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Nguyn Xun Bnh Minh\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38793:\"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Sng ngy 22/06/2025, cng ng Nha Trang WordPress  t chc thnh cng s kin Meetup ti Stockholm Co-working Space, quy t gn 30 thnh vin l cc lp trnh vin, marketer, ch doanh nghip, blogger v nhng ngi yu thch WordPress. y l s kin c mong ch nht nm ca cng ng, ni mi ngi c th cng nhau hc hi, tho lun v m rng quan h trong lnh vc pht trin website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Bi cnh nm 2025 chng kin s pht trin vt bc ca WordPress, khi nn tng ny chim gn mt na s lng website ton cu v p o cc i th trong mng CMS.iu ny cng cng c v th ca WordPress trong mt cng ng cng ngh ti Vit Nam ni chung v Nha Trang ni ring.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Chng trnh Meetup nm nay c u t k lng vi ba ch  ni bt:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Ti u Facebook Funnel  Dn li ngi dng v website WordPress</strong><br>Din gi Nguyn Ph Qu  phn tch chi tit cc bc xy dng phu chuyn i trn Facebook, t vic thu ht khch hng tim nng n vic a h v website WordPress  tng t l chuyn i v doanh thu.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>T ng ha sng to ni dung cho website WordPress vi AI v N8N</strong><br>Din gi Nguyn Minh Phng chia s cch ng dng tr tu nhn to v cng c N8N  t ng ha quy trnh to ni dung, gip qun tr vin website tit kim thi gian m vn m bo cht lng v s a dng ca ni dung.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Xy dng website bn sn phm s &amp; Ti u tc  website WordPress trn 